net.proteusframework.cms.controller

Class ParsedRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.cms.controller.ParsedRequest

  • public final class ParsedRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a parsed/resolved request from a user agent. This class encapsulates the CMS specific data related to the request.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
